s5722: Thirty-first year: Zheng besieged us, defeated them at Yong Qiu.
s5724: Sixteenth year: violated Chu, made peace with Wu.
s5727: Fifteenth year: besieged Song, defeated our army at Yong Qiu, attacked us.
s5733: Tenth year: with Wu attacked Qi.
s5734: Fourth year: Wu and Lu attacked us. Bao Zi killed Dao Gong, Qi people established his son Ren as Jian Gong.
s5735: Twenty-seventh year: sent Zhao Yang to attack Qi.
s5739: Eighth year: Confucius came from Chen.
s5745: Eleventh year: with Lu attacked Qi to rescue Chen. Executed the five officers.
s5749: Eleventh year: Qi attacked us. Ran You spoke, therefore welcomed Confucius, Confucius returned.
s5750: Qi Jian Gong first year: Lu and Wu defeated us.
s5755: Ninth year: Confucius returned to Lu.
s5761: Twelfth year: with Lu defeated Qi.
s5765: Twelfth year: assembled with Wu at Tuo Gao. Used field taxes.
s5769: Sixth year: Bai Gong Sheng repeatedly requested Zi Xi to attack Zheng, because of father's grudge.
s5771: Tenth year: the duke went to Jin, assembled with Wu at Tuo Gao.
s5777: Thirteenth year: assembled with Lu at Tuo Gao.
